Bio: Sirena is the stage name of Gerardo Leija Muñoz, a Mexican drag queen and performer, best known for being a contestant on Season 4 of the YouTube show La Más Draga.

Tiresias is the stage name of Tabris Berges, a Mexican drag queen and performer. She's one of the contestants and the winner of Season 1 of the YouTube show Versus Drag Queens: Edición México, the Mexican version of Versus Drag Queens. She also competed on Season 4 of the YouTube show La Más Draga.
